reviews.text: Very busy little restaurant, be prepared to queue for (around 15min) at peak times. Efficient but impersonal staff. Food is punchy with flavour and generously portioned. Prices are mid to high. The venue is pretty small and they have packed in as many tables as possible to maximise their turnover of diners, but seating is comfortable enough for a quick meal.
Quality improved a lot after the recent renovation less than 2 months ago. They provide high chairs so it's good for kids. Try it out when you are in Tsing Yi.

result.name: 青悅 · 越泰料理

reviews.text:
近排舊pokka個位開左間青悅·越泰料理, lunch一個飯/麵加飲品人均消費70-80幾蚊, 機場staff優惠免加一, 新裝修走簡潔路線, 枱同枱之間勁多空間坐得舒服好多, lunch menu好多款選擇: 炒飯, 泰式海南雞, 炭燒, 咖哩, 湯粉, 喇沙, 撈檬... 正.
>
L42. 炭燒豬頸肉配扎肉撈檬 (HKD72)
撈檬同魚露一齊黎, 樽魚露有大量辣椒🌶️但味道只係微辣, 怕辣嘅人都啱食. 豬頸肉有陣陣炭烤香, 打斜厚切肉質易咬, 唔覺好肥膩; 一碗有兩片扎肉, 細心位係塊扎肉有燒過, 食落香口得多. 大多數越式餐廳都易外一碟九層塔有啲直頭唔主動提供, li碗有一大枝, 夾埋所有魚露配料菜一齊食好有越南風味. 撈檬份量好足, 喺機場黎講真心足料飽肚.
> 
L43. 香茅雞全翼配扎肉撈檬 (HKD68)
雞全翼已經剪好兩件, 脆炸蒜同花生🥜粒又多種口感, 第一次喺機場食li間, 食物整得有心思, 可以encore！
> 
Lunch-熱檸水 
唔使加錢嘅餐飲有大路嘅汽水, 檸🍋茶, 水, 咖啡☕️, 仲有菜蜜. 另外加HKD12就可以轉特飲. 
> 
對自己好啲仲可以加HKD18來多款小食添.

result.name: 青悅

reviews.text: 環境舒適，食物不錯，晚餐吃了芒果軟殼蟹紙米卷，什菜煲，火車頭牛肉河粉
食物唔夠熱，坐地迫夾。

餐厅不大，菜的出品却是非常地道的越南口味。常常一个人来午餐，一碗火车头河粉，一份马拉盏炒椰菜，再叫一杯龙眼冰，可以很惬意的吃一个小时！
此外，一份冬阴功加一份青菜，配两碗米饭，也是二人就餐的好选择，海鲜冬荫功汤非常开胃，大大刺激食欲。yummy yummy
同老婆中午經過青衣城食飯，發現有間外觀唔錯嘅越南餐廳，佢嘅海鮮喇沙湯汁夠濃又唔係好難，馬莎問咖喱牛腩飯都唔錯！
推介必食咖哩配蒜蓉飽，炸春卷。

result.name: Hong Kong International Airport

reviews.text: On the whole a very good airport. Security is quick and efficient, and passport control is normally very quick too. There are a good selection of places to eat, despite ongoing renovations. The internal transit system is easy to use. No complaints.

One of the Large airports in the world. Its very wonderful shape of airport. Staffs are so friendly and helpful to passengers. The airport is very clean and fully well maintained. The view of airport is incredible. My experience was great here...

Great airport in town. Large varieties of food and great service at the Check In counter. Fast passenger flow. The terminals are large and comfy as well. The problems are the food can be quite expensive, and you may expect to walk a lot inside the airport. Also, it is far from Downtown, so you may catch a taxi or hop onto the Airport Express. Still pretty great tho. 4/5

Incredible!!! One of the amazing airports in the world. I don't know how it comes to their mind to build up an airport like this place. Its very big and wonderful shape airport. Staffs are so friendly and helpful to passengers. The airport is very clean and fully well maintained. The view of airport is incredible. My experience was great here. I was totally surprised. Love it❤

One of the best airports I have ever been. I fell in love with their relaxation corner in terminal 1. They are silent with ambient temperature and smooth lights. Even the room is perfumed with a soft smell of eucalyptus. They even have charging ports right next to the comfortable beds. With an amazing view of aircraft through the glass wall on one side.
